Additional bulb here.

294
00:25:09,574 --> 00:25:11,565
<i>[Laughter, Chattering]</i>

295
00:25:13,778 --> 00:25:15,609
Yeah.

296
00:25:19,818 --> 00:25:21,718
Yes. Whoo!

297
00:25:35,867 --> 00:25:37,892
[Sighs]

298
00:25:40,305 --> 00:25:42,239
Okay.
What? Now?

299
00:25:42,307 --> 00:25:44,741
What? You've got something
