321
00:28:01,413 --> 00:28:02,607
God.

322
00:28:06,317 --> 00:28:08,877
Oh, my God.

323
00:28:20,799 --> 00:28:23,029
Hey.

324
00:28:23,101 --> 00:28:26,229
<i>I need, uh,
two Social Security card,
uh, birth certificates.</i>

325
00:28:26,304 --> 00:28:28,238
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.

326
00:28:28,306 --> 00:28:31,434
Put your money away.
You said you could do this.
It's a problem?

327
00:28:31,509 --> 00:28:33,602
<i>You didn't hear?
You don't know?</i>

328
00:28:33,678 --> 00:28:35,805
No.
[Sighs]

329
00:28:36,815 --> 00:28:39,750
The ship went down, my friend.
What ship?

330
00:28:39,818 --> 00:28:42,150
