this morning. I'm sorry.

331
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:44,688
Wait, wait.
Uh, where did you find this?

332
00:28:45,690 --> 00:28:48,818
Who telling you...
Who's telling you this?
Please, don't get me in trouble.

333
00:29:09,214 --> 00:29:11,205
<i>[ Cell Phone Beeps On]</i>

334
00:29:12,383 --> 00:29:15,784
It's me. There is a shipping problem
with the last order.

335
00:29:15,854 --> 00:29:17,947
Something went wrong.

336
00:29:18,022 --> 00:29:20,320
We may not be able to fulfill it.

337
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:24,419
<i>[Woman]
What does he say
about securing our borders?</i>

338
00:29:24,496 --> 00:29:27,556
[Man]
Sir. Numbers?
Numbers of bodies saved?

339
00:29:28,633 --> 00:29:31,397
[Woman]
Sir, can you confirm this was
an illegal smuggling operation?

340
00:29:31,469 --> 00:29:34,097
<i>[Woman #2]
Have any dead bodies washed up
in the past two hours?</i>

341
00:29:34,172 --> 00:29:37,471
<i>[Man]
Are you going to make any arrests soon?
[Man #2] How about a statement?</i>

342
00:29:59,230 --> 00:30:03,098
<i>- [Phone Rings]
- [Man] Check the engine.
What is wrong with you?</i>

343
00:30:04,969 --> 00:30:08,029
Hey, Adam, I've been
calling you for 20 minutes.

344
00:30:09,307 --> 00:30:11,298
<i>Radio broke or something?</i>

345
00:30:12,777 --> 00:30:16,679
<i>- Yeah. Okay, I'll pick you up.
- Adam? You can't go in there.</i>

346
00:30:16,748 --> 00:30:20,081
<i>He's busy. He's on the phone.
You can't...
It's okay. I'll call you back.</i>

347
00:30:20,151 --> 00:30:22,642
<i>[Phone Ringing]</i>

348
00:30:25,256 --> 00:30:27,417
They've been calling you
for 20 minutes.

349
00:30:27,492 --> 00:30:30,393
