411
00:35:54,585 --> 00:35:56,849
- Hello.
- Hello?

412
00:35:56,921 --> 00:35:59,014
Dad.
Tyler?

413
00:35:59,090 --> 00:36:01,581
Hey. What are you up to?
Oh, you know.

414
00:36:01,659 --> 00:36:04,253
I'm good. How's Mom?
She's good.

415
00:36:05,263 --> 00:36:07,595
Yeah? How's the bird?

416
00:36:08,599 --> 00:36:11,466
- It's dead.
- [Chuckles]
''It's dead.''

417
00:36:11,536 --> 00:36:13,595
Of course it's dead.

418
00:36:14,772 --> 00:36:17,935
- Do you want to talk to Mom?
- Sure, sure, sure.
Put her on.

419
00:36:18,943 --> 00:36:20,843
Hey.
Hi, babe.

420
00:36:20,912 --> 00:36:22,846
Happy Thanksgiving.
Is it?

421
00:36:22,914 --> 00:36:26,008
Yeah. Yeah, yeah.

422
00:36:26,083 --> 00:36:28,881
So, you know, we've had better.

423
00:36:28,953 --> 00:36:32,650
- You want me to speak to him?
I'll set him straight.
- No, no, no. He's okay.

424
00:36:32,723 --> 00:36:34,748
Just hold off on that for now.

425
00:36:36,460 --> 00:36:39,588
I'm gonna be out of touch
for a couple days.
Just maybe a week.

426
00:36:39,664 --> 00:36:43,031
But, uh, I'll call as soon as
I get to a phone I can use, okay?

427
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:46,900
Listen, be careful, okay?
Always, babe.

428
00:36:51,309 --> 00:36:53,243
Hey, I love you.

429
00:36:53,311 --> 00:36:56,303
Everything I'm doing here
is for you and Tyler.
Remember that.

430
00:36:56,380 --> 00:36:59,713
Okay? Even when
it gets tough. Okay?

431
00:36:59,784 --> 00:37:02,412
Mike.

432
00:37:03,721 --> 00:37:06,713
Mike.
[Disconnect Signal]

433
00:37:09,227 --> 00:37:11,218
Mom?

434
00:37:11,295 --> 00:37:13,286
[Sighs]
We got cut off.

435
00:37:32,216 --> 00:37:34,150
Huh.

436
00:37:56,807 --> 00:37:59,332
You know what I'd really love?

437
00:37:59,410 --> 00:38:01,742
<i>[Man On TV]
Twice the size it was
